    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Social, political, and economic system of racial segregation, assigning rights to classes of people based on their racial background, supremacy being granted to those of white European extraction, with laws limiting the political participation and economic advancement of those of African, Asian, and mixed race.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sistema social, político y económico de segregación social, que otorga derechos a clases de personas basándose en sus antecedentes raciales, el liderazgo es garantizado a aquellos blancos de ascendencia europea, con leyes que limitan la participación social y progreso económico de aquellos de raza africana, asiática y mixta.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sociaal, politiek en economisch systeem van rassenscheiding dat rechten aan klassen van mensen toekent op basis van hun ras; superioriteit wordt toegekend aan mensen van blanke Europese afkomst, en wetten worden uitgevaardigd die de politieke deelneming en economische vooruitgang van Afrikanen, Aziaten en van andere, gemengde, rassen belemmeren.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052381/Van Dale Engels-Nederlands (1989)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>意指實施種族隔離的社會、政治及經濟制度。在種族隔離制度下，人民所能擁有的權利是依照其種族背景來劃分；擁有歐洲白人血統者能享有至高的權力地位，而非裔、亞裔與種族混合血統者則受到法律限制其參與政治及提升經濟能力的機會。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
